      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 1,
        "content": [
          "Diminutives make things smaller or cuter.",
          "Add -chen or -lein to any noun:",
          "",
          "KEY RULE: ALL diminutives become NEUTER!",
          "(This is why 'das Mädchen' = girl is neuter)",
          "",
          "-CHEN (more common):",
          "der Hund → das Hündchen (little dog)",
          "die Katze → das Kätzchen (kitten)",
          "das Brot → das Brötchen (bread roll)",
          "der Bruder → das Brüderchen (little brother)",
          "",
          "-LEIN (more literary/poetic):",
          "das Buch → das Büchlein (little book)",
          "der Vogel → das Vögelein (little bird)",
          "",
          "UMLAUT OFTEN ADDED:",
          "a → ä, o → ö, u → ü",
          "Haus → Häuschen, Hund → Hündchen"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion zweiundzwanzig"
      }
    ]
  },
